Invocation Name: christian financial
Developer Terms of Use
des:
Now you can ask for your balance and recent transaction history from any Amazon Alexa-enabled device. You can enable the skill by saying "Alexa, enable the Christian Financial skill" or by enabling it in the skills section of the Alexa app. 

Once you've enabled the skill, you can ask such questions as:
 - "What's my checking account balance?"
 - "What are my recent transactions?"
 - "What are my account balances?"
Use of this skill will allow financial information to be read aloud or displayed visually.
